Package: truncatedFGLM
Title: Truncated Functional Generalized Linear Model
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
              person("Xi", "Liu", role = c("aut")),
              person("Chau", "Tran", email = "chautran@ucsb.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
              person("Alexander", "Petersen", role = c("aut")))
Description: An implementation of the methodologies described in Xi Liu, Afshin A. Divani, and Alexander Petersen (2022) <https://doi.org/10.1016/j.csda.2022.107421>, including 
                truncated functional linear and truncated functional logistic regression models.
